LEX The Assessor.

"First Person" is a person.
"Assessor" is a person.
"Keystone" is a person.
"Metric Report" is a text.
"Metric Fresh" is a binary.
"Frontier Stale" is a binary.

The First Person appoints the Assessor, and appoints the Keystone.

CLAUSE: Rerun.
The Assessor may declare Metric Fresh.

CLAUSE: Report.
The Assessor may, if Metric Fresh is declared: send the Metric Report to the Keystone.

CLAUSE: Flag.
The Assessor may declare Frontier Stale.
